    "name": "Dark Deity",
    "steam_appid": 1374840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/e2dd153536996fac98f20d3d56ee3666.avif?t=1769810723\" width=780 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特拉扎埃尔。一个被背誓者、战争贩子以及掌握禁忌奥术秘密之人撕裂的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个紧抓最后一丝希望的世界。数百年前的“大灾厄”摧毁了曾经辉煌的文明，使其彻底崩塌。往日的伟大帝王不复存在，取而代之的是狭隘的国王，他们发动徒劳而鲁莽的战争，在古老遗迹中翻找残骸，宛如被美化的拾荒者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >率领四名来自布鲁克斯特德军事学院的学生。该学院因国王瓦里克的神秘命令而被关闭。德利亚王国的统治者正准备撕毁一项延续千年的条约，而布鲁克斯特德的学生正是理想的炮灰……然而，这四名士兵注定不只是被送上绞肉机的牺牲品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们尚未知晓，但他们将改变历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/f8c772221ad0f6043b46a5bdd045f893.avif?t=1769810723\" width=780 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/64c94afca5fc3c714e6ca4143e3cf507.poster.avif?t=1769810723\" width=780 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/64c94afca5fc3c714e6ca4143e3cf507.webm?t=1769810723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/64c94afca5fc3c714e6ca4143e3cf507.mp4?t=1769810723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个被无尽战争与魔法灾变撕裂的世界中，带领士兵投入战斗。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在横跨28个章节的手工制作回合制战斗场景中奋战，让新兵成长为老兵。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >考验你的战术能力。机动、进攻、突破——也许还能扭转战争的局势。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >塑造传奇的崛起，将一群生涩的新兵打造成神话般的英雄团队。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/55d042f552d0b216838f637b8c3a17a0.avif?t=1769810723\" width=780 height=180 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/b8e80acc5507dc7680caead899026df8.poster.avif?t=1769810723\" width=780 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/b8e80acc5507dc7680caead899026df8.webm?t=1769810723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/b8e80acc5507dc7680caead899026df8.mp4?t=1769810723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心培养你的小队，在漫长的战斗中存活下来，并在看似绝望的世界中带来改变。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从30名可游玩角色中组建小队，每位角色都有独特的背景、性格与动机，对他们进行训练，并从54种各具特色的职业中进行选择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为每支队伍装备数百种武器与法术，从简单的刀剑与投射物，到能够释放毁灭世界魔法的古老异界神器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失败并不意味着永久死亡，但代价依然存在：每一次倒下都会造成重伤、属性惩罚，并削弱你的小队。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/14a66eaff219e1e9f7a5132de2c8c8d0.avif?t=1769810723\" width=780 height=170 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/f3e8d2e2305145629a71e23cf27a8353.poster.avif?t=1769810723\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/f3e8d2e2305145629a71e23cf27a8353.webm?t=1769810723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1374840/extras/f3e8d2e2305145629a71e23cf27a8353.mp4?t=1769810723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在被大灾厄摧毁的世界中，希望是一种稀缺资源——所幸，这些英雄心中充满希望。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战命运，率领这支非同寻常的英雄队伍，改变世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见证角色在战场上建立羁绊，并通过400段独立对话推动关系的发展。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记住：任何英雄都能带来改变——只要他们活得够久。</p></li></ul>",
